What is TechLecture!?

TechLecture! is a game-based learning platform that makes it easy
to create, share and play learning games or trivia quizzes in
minutes. Unleash the fun in classrooms, offices and living
rooms!

How it works

Create

Create a fun learning game in minutes – we call these ‘TechLectures’.
The format and number of questions is up to you. Add videos, images and
diagrams to your questions to amplify engagement.

Play

TechLectures are best played in a group setting. To join a game, you need a
unique PIN. If you’re the game host, you need a big screen. Players
answer on their own devices, while questions are displayed on a shared
screen. In addition to live games, you can also send TechLecture challenges
that players complete at their own pace – for example, for homework
or remote training.

Share

After a game, encourage players to create and share their own
TechLectures! With one of our premium plans for schools or business, you
can co-create games with your colleagues and save time on finding
relevant TechLectures for your class or training session.

Played around the world in classrooms, offices and living rooms

By teachers and students

Millions of teachers and students unleash the
magic of learning with TechLecture! Introduce new
topics, review, reward, and collect data for
formative assessment.

By office superheroes

Make learning awesome in a business setting, too!
Companies of all sizes use TechLecture! in training,
presentations, team building and events.

By families and friends

Birthdays, weddings, holidays, game nights,
family dinners, trivia TechLecture! is the secret
ingredient that will make any party or gathering
even more awesome.
